<li><span class="info">(<a href="../sle2021/index.html">SLE 2021</a>)</span> <em>Coauthored <a href="../sle2021/paper13.html">Getting grammars into shape for block-based editors</a></em> (<a href="../profile/MauricioVeranoMerino.html"><span class="info">Mauricio Verano Merino</span></a>, <a href="../profile/TomBeckmann.html">Tom Beckmann</a>, <a href="../profile/TijsvanderStorm.html">Tijs van der Storm</a>, <a href="../profile/RobertHirschfeld.html">Robert Hirschfeld</a>, <a href="../profile/JurgenVinju.html">Jurgen Vinju</a>) </li>
