<li><span class="info">(<a href="../sle2022/index.html">SLE 2022</a>)</span> <em>Coauthored <a href="../sle2022/paper15.html">A Language-Parametric Approach to Exploratory Programming Environments</a></em> (<a href="../profile/LThomasvanBinsbergen.html">L. Thomas van Binsbergen</a>, <a href="../profile/DamianFrölich.html">Damian Frölich</a>, <a href="../profile/MauricioVeranoMerino.html"><span class="info">Mauricio Verano Merino</span></a>, <a href="../profile/JoeyLai.html">Joey Lai</a>, <a href="../profile/PierreJeanjean.html">Pierre Jeanjean</a>, <a href="../profile/TijsvanderStorm.html">Tijs van der Storm</a>, <a href="../profile/BenoîtCombemale.html">Benoît Combemale</a>, <a href="../profile/OlivierBarais.html">Olivier Barais</a>) </li>
